</span></li><li class=\"\" htag=\"li\"><span class=\"x\">‘Where shall we eat?’ ‘I'm not bothered.’ <span class=\"gloss\" htag=\"span\" hclass=\"gloss\">(= I don't mind where we go.)</span></span></li></ul>      </li></ol></span> <span class=\"idm-g\" sk=\"cantbebothered\" id=\"bother_idmg_2\"><div class=\"top-container\"><div class=\"top-g\" id=\"bother_topg_4\"><div class=\"webtop\"><span class=\"idm\" id=\"bother_idm_2\">can’t be bothered (to do something)</span> </div></div></div><ol class=\"sense_single\" htag=\"ol\"><li class=\"sense\" hclass=\"sense\" id=\"bother_sng_5\" htag=\"li\"><span class=\"sensetop\" hclass=\"sensetop\" htag=\"span\"><span class=\"def\" hclass=\"def\" htag=\"span\">used to say that you do not want to spend time and/or energy doing something</span></span><ul class=\"examples\" htag=\"ul\" hclass=\"examples\"><li class=\"\" htag=\"li\"><span class=\"x\">I should really do some work this weekend but I can't be bothered.</span></li><li class=\"\" htag=\"li\"><span class=\"x\">All this has happened because you couldn't be bothered to give me the message.</span></li></ul>      </li></ol></span> <span class=\"idm-g\" id=\"hot_idmg_14\" sk=\"hotandbothered\"><div class=\"top-container\"><div class=\"top-g\" id=\"hot_topg_7\"><div class=\"webtop\"><span class=\"idm\" id=\"hot_idm_5\">(all) hot and bothered</span> </div></div></div><ol class=\"sense_single\" htag=\"ol\"><li class=\"sense\" htag=\"li\" id=\"hot_sng_34\" hclass=\"sense\"><span class=\"sensetop\" htag=\"span\" hclass=\"sensetop\"><span class=\"labels\" htag=\"span\" hclass=\"labels\">(informal)</span></span> <span class=\"def\" htag=\"span\" hclass=\"def\">in a state of worry or stress because you are under too much pressure, have a problem, are trying to hurry, etc.</span>      </li></ol></span> <span class=\"idm-g\" id=\"bother_idmg_3\" sk=\"notbotheryourselfheadwith\"><div class=\"top-container\"><div class=\"top-g\" id=\"bother_topg_5\"><div class=\"webtop\"><span class=\"idm\" 